OL,6,FThe cause of death will be determined
OL,7,Fis not yet known and will be
OL,8,Fdetermined by a medical examination,
OL,9,Frace organisers said.
OL,11,F"It is with great sadness that The
OL,12,FGreat Run Company confirms the death
OL,13,Fof a participant at the Great Bristol
OL,14,FRun on Sunday, 11 May 2025", the
OL,15,Fstatement read.
OL,17,F"Jon Devereux, aged 28, collapsed
OL,18,Fduring the event, received immediate
OL,19,Fmedical treatment, and later passed
OL,20,Faway in hospital. His next of kin have
OL,21,Fbeen informed.
