OL,6,FMr Devereux played Rugby for Chester
OL,7,FRUFC. The club said in a statement:
OL,8,F"It is with deep sadness that we share
OL,9,Fthe tragic news of the passing of Jon
OL,10,FDevereux, who suffered a heart attack
OL,11,Fwhile competing in the Bristol Half
OL,12,FMarathon at the weekend.
OL,14,F"Jon was a talented athlete who played
OL,15,Fsenior rugby for Chester, and his
OL,16,Fenergy, spirit, and sportsmanship left
OL,17,Fa lasting impression on all who knew
OL,18,Fhim.
