OL,6,FA spokesperson for Great Western Air
OL,7,FAmbulance charity confirmed: "Whilst
OL,8,Fproviding emergency medical cover at
OL,9,Fthe Great Bristol Run on Sunday 11
OL,10,FMay, our critical care crew were
OL,11,Fcalled to provide immediate assistance
OL,12,Fto a patient who sadly collapsed at
OL,13,Fthe event.
OL,15,F"A Critical Care Doctor and Specialist
OL,16,FParamedic treated the patient at the
OL,17,Fscene, before travelling with them to
OL,18,Fhospital.
